  m_text: The logical architecture describes the basic structure and the mode of
    action of the system. it is part of the principle solution of mechatronic systems.
    the effect principles found are collected together with the first constructive
    solution possibilities in a morphological box. The relationships and elements
    can be classified and different ways of looking at the model are possible. The
    effect structure is at the same time a system architecture.
